<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Binance will distribute the token vouchers to winners on June 23. The OPG voucher rewards will expire within 21 days after distribution. To claim your rewards, log in to your Binance Wallet and redeem your token voucher rewards via Profile &gt; Rewards Hub.</span></p>
